<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>U of H Caeti Demo:Live Version</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY>
<H1>Caeti Demo</H1>
<H1>University of Hawaii</H1>

<HR SIZE="12">
<H2>Your requirements</H2>
<P>Use the following questionnaire to specify your requirements.  Don't
worry about not answering questions that aren't relevant to your plan.</P>

<FORM Method="POST" ACTION="cgi-bin/run-demo.cgi">

<HR>
<H3><I>At the start of the exercise...</I></H3>
<P>Indicate the platoon's starting formation:</P>
<TABLE>
<TR><TD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="theStartForm" VALUE="coil">Coil</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="theStartForm"
				VALUE="herringbone">Herringbone</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="theStartForm"
				VALUE="halted-ctf">Halted Column</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="theStartForm"
				VALUE="halted-wltf">Halted Wedge</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
<P>Indicate the coordinates of the starting location:
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="theStartCoords" SIZE="8" MAXLENGTH="8">
(e.g., NK123456)</P>

<HR>
<H3><I>In the middle...</I></H3>
<P>Indicate the drills you want to be included in the exercise (you can
require that a drill appear more than once by entering a number in its
text field):</P>
<BR>
<TABLE>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT><TH>Battle drills</TH><TH></TH>
	<TH ROWSPAN=8><PRE>          </PRE></TH>
	<TH>Traveling formations</TH><TH></TH>
</TR>
<TR><TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="vfaa">Air attack</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="vfaa-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="ctf">Column</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="ctf-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
</TR>
<TR><TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="cfs">Contact drill</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="cfs-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="sctf">Staggered column</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="sctf-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
</TR>
<TR><TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="ad">Action drill</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="ad-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="wltf">Wedge</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="wltf-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
</TR>
<TR><TH ALIGN=LEFT>Traveling techniques</TH>
    <TD></TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="eltf">Echelon</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="eltf-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
</TR>
<TR><TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="ttm">Traveling technique</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="ttm-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="vtf">Vee</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="vtf-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
</TR>
<TR><TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="totm">Traveling overwatch</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="totm-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="ltf">Line</TD>
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="ltf-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2"></TD>
</TR>
<TR><TD><INPUT TYPE="checkbox" NAME="botm">Bounding overwatch
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="text"     NAME="botm-num" SIZE="2" MAXLENGTH="2">
    <TD></TD>
    <TD></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

<HR>
<H3><I>At the end...</I></H3>
<P>Indicate the platoon's ending formation:</P>
<TABLE>
<TR><TD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="theEndForm" VALUE="coil">Coil
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="theEndForm" VALUE="herringbone">Herringbone
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="theEndForm" VALUE="halted-ctf">Halted Column
    <TD><INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="theEndForm" VALUE="halted-wltf">Halted Wedge
</TR>
</TABLE>
<P>Indicate the coordinates of the ending location:
<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="theEndCoords" SIZE="8" MAXLENGTH="8">
(e.g., NK123456)</P>

<BR>
<P><INPUT TYPE="SUBMIT" VALUE="Generate scenarios">
<INPUT TYPE="RESET" VALUE="Clear this form"></P>

<HR SIZE="12">
<H2>One scenario generated for your requirements</H2>
<P>The output will go here.</P>
<INPUT TYPE="SUBMIT" VALUE="Show a different scenario">
<BR>

</FORM>

<HR SIZE="12">
<a href="http://spectra.eng.hawaii.edu/~pautler/Caeti/demo.html">
Back to the Demo homepage
</a>

</BODY>
</HTML>